The paper focuses on fashion image retrieval, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV). The use of Capsule Networks and dynamic routing also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also involves feature extraction and similarity matching, which are common tasks in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG).
